text.tspan: Name: Xenos
Age: 30
Status: Alive (maybe)
Role: Wanted
Documentation:
Click this to exit
Xander was a pro swimmer champion
known for being rude. A group of his
despisers, made up of his previous
contestants who lost to him, thought
for some reason that dumping 4
buckets of live pirhanas into the pool
was a funny prank. Clearly, it wasnt.
Xander got eaten through, and died.
The next day the people who had the
pirhanas all died, and Xanders body
went missing. We heard Doctor Zenzo
talking about him before as they
are brothers, and from that we assume
he could be alive, and Zenzos
theory about his immortal genes could
be true. We want him, if he is alive.
DONK
Industries
